site_name: Part Of The Former Barclays Sports Ground
description: Details of self-closing external doors pursuant to condition 18 of planning permission ref: 183238FUL dated 21/11/2018 for: Construction of part single, part two and part four-storey building for use as a 6.5 Form Entry Secondary School (1,330 pupils) to east of site; installation of multi-use games area; vehicle access widening on Park View Road; and associated refuse and cycle parking storage, hardstanding and boundary treatment works
